        "timestamp": "2019-07-16 17:00:22.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIf you run git-review without any specific arg, it will automatically rebase vs master and then will fail. This file must be considered as incorrect because the wrong branch is set.\n\nIt should be the first step right after creating the branch.",
        "patchset_number": 1
